OL,3,CTributes to 'fiercely loving' man
OL,4,Cafter Boxing Day death after alleged
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FTributes have been paid to a 37-year-
OL,8,Fold Cardiff man who died on Boxing Day
OL,9,Ffollowing an alleged assault several
OL,10,Fdays earlier.
OL,12,FColm Marcus Boston from Heath is
OL,13,Fbelieved to have been assaulted on
OL,14,FPentyrch Street, Cathays, at around
OL,15,F6.15pm on Monday 22 December. Three
OL,16,Fmen have been arrested in connection
OL,17,Fwith the incident and have been
OL,18,Freleased on bail pending further
OL,19,Fenquiries.
