OL,3,CTributes to 'fiercely loving' man
OL,4,Cafter Boxing Day death after alleged
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,F"Following the incident on Monday 22
OL,8,FDecember, Colm sadly passed away in
OL,9,Fhospital on Boxing Day. We are being
OL,10,Fsupported by a Family Liaison Officer
OL,11,Fand are grateful for the compassion
OL,12,Fshown to us during this incredibly
OL,13,Fdifficult time.
