OL,3,CTributes to 'fiercely loving' man
OL,4,Cafter Boxing Day death after alleged
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,F"We would like to express our
OL,8,Fheartfelt appreciation to the nurses
OL,9,Fand doctors at University Hospital of
OL,10,FWales, who were absolutely amazing in
OL,11,Ftheir care, professionalism, and
OL,12,Funwavering support of Colm and our
OL,13,Ffamily. Their kindness and dedication
OL,14,Fwill never be forgotten.
OL,16,F"We thank everyone for their support,
OL,17,Frespect, and understanding as we come
OL,18,Fto terms with this devastating loss."
