OL,7,FSouth Wales Police say a 51-year-old
OL,8,Fman from Mynachdy, a 47-year-old man
OL,9,Ffrom Adamsdown and a 60-year-old man
OL,10,Ffrom Cathays have been released on
OL,11,Fbail pending further enquiries.
OL,13,FThe force is continuing to appeal for
OL,14,Fany CCTV and dash-cam footage from
OL,15,FMaindy Road, Pentyrch Street,
OL,16,FWhitchurch Road, and Cathays Terrace,
OL,17,Ffrom between 4pm and 6.30pm on Monday
OL,18,F22 December.
